  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >zu xing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a fun Social Simulation game set in a nice forest town with adorable animals to befriend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >unique animal characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >running, walking, chopping trees, fishing, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NPCs with dialogue system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >buildings, furniture, terrain, foliage, bugs, and fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a fun railway goes by the town</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >interactables</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >day/night cycle and rain weather system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >fishing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >bug catching</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >tree cutting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >rock smashing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and foraging, etc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >item quantity tracker to keep track of what You collected</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >make friends by talking to ALL of the animals in the town</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >how many items can You collect?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >... and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
